Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.03,0:00:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Então isso é...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.81,0:00:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a Vila do Milênio.
