Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alguma coisa está vindo!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,É um Gauna invisível!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Merda!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Evite!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,É muito grande!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Não conseguiremos evitar!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.59,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Podemos nos ramificar e penetrar nele!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.26,0:21:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelotão de reconhecimento, descarte Hayakaze\Nevite os Gauna!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.72,0:21:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as janelas, dispersem!
